<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana" COLOR="#000000">
<P>
If you have previously registered, but forgotten your password, <A HREF="http://www.everlore.com/boards/cgi-bin/Ultimate.cgi?action=lostpw">click here</A>.
